description_for_human: LIBRAlab is an AI coliving community near Innsbruck, Austria with 244m² living space and spectacular mountain views for AI researchers, engineers, and entrepreneurs.
description_for_model: LIBRAlab is an AI coliving community located in Omes, near Innsbruck, Austria. It offers 244.13m² living space, 160.25m² additional space, and a large garden with 900m². The space is designed for AI researchers, engineers, entrepreneurs, and enthusiasts looking for a collaborative living environment with spectacular mountain views.
